<h1>Custom Properties</h1>
<p>These variables are used internally by M- and are meant for direct use when creating custom styles.</p>
<h2 id="demo">Demo</h2>
<code-sample>
  <style>
    @import "../node_modules/m-/dist/custom-props.css";
    #foo { background-color: var(--color-gray-2) }
  </style>
  <div id="foo" class="pad-all-lg">I'm styled with a custom property</div>
</code-sample>
